  Rick> This is dangerous; I have to remember to re-scan each
  Rick> folder I enter. Is there a safeguard for this?

Nope.  Regenerate the cache in the script

	for f in `folders -fast -r`
	do
		echo sorting $f ...
		sortm +$f
		scan `mhpath +`/$f/.xmhcache
	done

